"      </a>",
"      and",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?1/56/1923?source=see_link\">",
"       \"Patient information: Gallbladder removal (cholecystectomy) (The Basics)\"",
"      </a>",
"      )",
"     </li>",
"     <li>",
"      Beyond the Basics topics (see",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?7/21/7507?source=see_link\">",
